ddleware for comprehensive bot protection\r\n  - `options.backendUrl` (optional): Backend API base URL for pricing, public key lookups, and analytics.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## ðŸ‘¤ Maintainer\r\n- Arun â€” [x.com/0xarun](https://x.com/0xarun) | [linkedin.com/in/0xarun](https://linkedin.com/in/0xarun) ","readmeFilename":"README.md"}